-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-29/faber-says-ecb-loans-to-only-help-short-term-handelsblatt-says.html
Marc Faber  said the  European Central
Bank ’s latest loans to European banks will only calm markets
short-term, lead to inflation in the long-term and push banks’
funding problems into the future,  Handelsblatt  said in a preview
of a story that will run tomorrow, citing the fund manager.  To contact the reporter on this story:
